http://loclhost:8080/spring-mvc/login

spring-mvc

1)Dispatcher servlet -> Front Controller ->handles incoming http request and forward it to controller

2)/login-> LoginController(handler) -> this controller is used on the the link

3)view resolver
login-> /WEB-INF/views/login.jsp -> prefix and suffix  for login set in todoServlet.

login.jsp -> View

/WEB-INF/views/login.jsp

model -> anything we want to pass from controller to view model is used.